<section class="we-planned py-5 bg-vh-2"> <div class="container-fluid"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-5"> <img src="assets/v2/static_page/images/we-planed-to-create.webp" loading="lazy" width="" height="" class="img-fluid w-100" alt="We planned to create one platform where patients will find answers"> </div> <div class="col-md-7 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center mt-4 mt-md-0"> <h2 class="fs-3 fw-bolder">We planned to create one platform where patients will find answers to most common questions crossing their mind:</h2> <ul class="list-w-circle mb-2"> <li>Who is the right doctor for my medical problem?</li> <li>Where are the best hospitals available?</li> <li>Can I afford the treatment I am looking for?</li> <li>What are the success rates for the procedure?</li> <li>What will be my life after the surgery?</li> <li>What will recovery look like?</li> <li>And many more</li> </ul> <p class="mb-0">This process becomes more difficult when you realise you have to travel to a foreign country for medical treatment. That’s where Vaidam Health comes in !</p> </div> </div> </div> </div>
</section>


<section class="how-do-we-help py-5 bg-theam-2"> <div class="container-fluid"> <div class="container py-0"> <div class="row align-items-center"> <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-6"> <h2 class="fs-3">How do we help our patients in their journey for care?</h2> <p class="lh-base">We have medically trained experts working in Vaidam who will collect medical history, reports from our patients and share the medical opinion and cost estimates from treating doctors in patients preferred destination.<br>Once a patient chooses the doctor for themselves, our team assists with travel logistics – Visa application, airport transfers, hotels, money exchange etc.<br>Having helped more than 100,000 + patients, our team is well equipped to find the right choice for our patients.</p> <h2 class="fs-3">How have we grown in our journey so far?</h2> <p class="lh-base">Vaidam started in January 2016. Since then we are now a team of 100+ full time employees working day in and out to assist our patients. Starting with India as a destination for treatment in 2016, we grew our hospital network to more countries in the world where patients travel seeking medical care. We now offer medical treatments in 8+ top destinations in the world – namely – India, Thailand, Turkey, Germany, UAE, South Korea, Tunisia, Egypt.<br>Patients from 125+ countries have travelled safely and happily with Vaidam to their preferred destinations.<br>We strive to be the world’s # 1 company of choice for patients travelling for medical treatment.</p> <h2 class="fs-3">What treatments do we expertise in handling?</h2> <p class="lh-base">We have handled patients for more than 50 specialities. So whether you are British citizen looking for Dental or Cosmetic Surgery in Turkey; a concerned parent for a child with “hole in the heart” in Gambia looking for treatment in India; a Bangladeshi couple struggling to have a child and planning for IVF in Thailand; an Omani family deciding to seek cancer care in Germany for your loved ones, we are there with you.<br>We have in-depth experience in handling – Cancer cases, Brain and Spine surgery, Cardiac Surgery, Organ Transplant (Liver, Kidney), Bone Marrow Transplant for blood cancers, Orthopaedic and Joints replacements, Urology, Infertility (IVF), Ophthalmology, Dental and Cosmetics among others.</p> </div> <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-5"> <div class="slider-form bg-theam"> <div class="dynamic_content"> <div class="main_container"> <style type="text/css"> .primary-form {
